messages.text: It’s late but yeah. What’s up?
I miss you too babe. Why are you scared?
just watched a horror movie haha.
No idea lol it was just on tv. Girl gets stalked and murdered in her house when she’s alone.
haha i think you'll be alright sarah. It’s just a movie.
Yeah i know but im just getting super paranoid. Turned the light on in my room haha.
Anyone in the house with you?
i know lol. they won’t be back until tomorrow night
Well just make sure everything’s locked and you’ll be fine
The front door. It’s like a little bit open but i could’ve swore i closed it all the way
maybe it just didn’t catch all the way, not a big deal.
no its weird, i definitely closed it. I’m sure
you’re just scared and are overthinking everything
no one actually does anything like in those movies
You told me you were being paranoid
you’re fine, really. Nothing to worry about
It’s late here. I should really go to bed soon babe.
don’t leave me corey. I need someone to talk to.
Ok ok I’ll stay don’t worry.
You should try going to sleep soon.
There’s a lot of sounds out there you only notice them when you’re scared
It was like a bump. From downstairs.
Don’t you keep the cat downstairs?
I think I'm gonna check it out
Why? do you think it’s dangerous?
You’ll freak yourself out. Just try to forget about it
Babe that movie just freaked you out.
Our town’s way too boring for that stuff to happen haha
The bump. even louder this time.
Someone could have known that I was home alone.
Turn on some lights. That way you’ll see nothing’s wrong.
The guest room door is open.
So? You must have left it open.
It’s been closed for a while.
I cant think why it'd be open.
Your parents might have been looking for something.
You should really try to get some sleep.
and the cat is right here with me.
It could just be the pipes creaking. They do that when you don’t use them for awhile
The floorboards are creaking not the pipes
It could be the house setting in.
It came from the kitchen. I’m going back up.
you still think there’s someone there?
Oh come on, it’s never the wind. Someone’s in the house.
I think I’m going to call stacy, see if she can pick me up.
It’s almost 2 am sarah, you shouldn’t bother her.
yes. and you watched a scary movie, you’re alone, so you keep thinking it’s going to happen to you.
if you were any real danger you’d call the police, not talk to me.
I’m going to check out what’s that noise upstairs.
Not because I think someone’s there just don’t give yourself a panic attack or anything.
I don’t see anything. The shadows of the trees in the backyards are pretty creepy though.
But there’s nothing to be afraid of, right?
It’s like some times the trees sway but only certain branches. Like the shadows are moving.
That happens. Could also be clouds covering up the moonlight.
I can’t stay in this kitchen. I keep hearing steps in the distance. I don’t like the shadows.
The mind always plays tricks when you’re scared. Remember the cat?
Ok I’m starting to feel silly about all this haha
Alright thats better. Are you heading to bed now?
Yeah. Thanks babe you’ve been such a good help. I love you.
I think I’m gonna turn the light on in my room though haha it can’t hurt.
Wait, wasn’t the light already on in your room? Why was it off?
